“That will do,” said Martha quietly.

He stopped speaking, sitting naked on the edge of the bed and staring at the floor.

“Oh, darling, darling,” she said cheerlessly and impetuously. “Does this matter? Don’t you feel the days are going by while we keep aimlessly discussing things, not knowing where to begin? Don’t you see, this way we’ll drive ourselves to the point where one fine day we’ll simply pounce on 